<h1 class="hero-h">How a B2B agency <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">2x'd content output.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A 14-person B2B marketing agency serving SaaS clients. They were turning down work because production capacity was capped by senior writer time. After a Treetop engagement, output doubled and margins expanded meaningfully. Here is how.</p>
<div class="headline-metric">
<div class="metric-num">2.1×</div>
<div class="metric-label">increase in monthly content output across the agency, with same headcount</div>
</div>
